Individual




Richard Lee Phegley



Mr. Richard L. Phegley is CFO & Principal Accounting Officer at Invesco Mortgage Capital, Inc. Mr. Phegley was previously employed as Senior Manager by Arthur Andersen LLP and Senior Manager by KPMG LLP. He also served on the board at Archon Group LP. He received his undergraduate degree from Baylor University and a graduate degree from the University of Houston.



