                                                    REIT Stocks on Investors' Radar -- Drive Shack, Empire State Realty Trust, Investors Real Estate Trust, and Invesco Mortgage Capital
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    6:15 AM ET 07/24/2017
                                                


NEW YORK, July 24, 2017 If you want a Stock Review on DS, ESRT, IRET, or IVR then come over to http://dailystocktracker.com/register/ and sign up for your free customized report today. http://dailystocktracker.com/register/ Drive Shack . New York-based Drive Shack Inc.'s (DS) stock finished last Friday's session flat at $3.02. A total volume of 503,512 shares was traded. http://dailystocktracker.com...

















                                                    Invesco Mortgage Capital Inc. to Present at the JMP Securities 2017 Financial Services and Real Estate Conference
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    10:30 AM ET 06/16/2017
                                                


ATLANTA, June 16, 2017 Invesco Mortgage Capital Inc. (IVR) is scheduled to present at the JMP Securities 2017 Financial Services and Real Estate Conference to be held in New York City on June 22, 2017, at approximately 1:15 p.m. Eastern Time. John Anzalone, Chief Executive Officer, and Jason Marshall, Chief Investment Officer, are scheduled to speak.

















                                                    Invesco Mortgage Capital Inc. Announces Quarterly Common and Preferred Stock Dividends
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    4:15 PM ET 06/15/2017
                                                


ATLANTA, June 15, 2017 /PRNewswire/ -- Invesco Mortgage Capital Inc. (IVR) today announced that its Board of Directors declared quarterly dividends on shares of its common stock and Series A and Series B preferred stock. Common Stock Dividend The Company's Board of Directors today declared a cash dividend of $0.40 per share of common stock for the second quarter of 2017.

















                                                    Invesco Mortgage Capital Inc. to present at KBW Mortgage Finance and Asset Management Conference
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    10:32 AM ET 05/25/2017
                                                


ATLANTA, May 25, 2017 Invesco Mortgage Capital Inc. (IVR) is scheduled to present at the KBW Mortgage Finance and Asset Management Conference to be held in New York City on June 1, 2017, at approximately 3:20 p.m. Eastern Time. John Anzalone, Chief Executive Officer, and Jason Marshall, Chief Investment Officer, are scheduled to speak.

















                                                    BRIEF-Invesco Mortgage Capital reports Q1 basic earnings $0.78 per common share
                                                


                                                    Reuters – 
                                                    5:08 PM ET 05/04/2017
                                                


Invesco Mortgage Capital Inc (IVR). * Invesco Mortgage Capital Inc (IVR). reports first quarter 2017 financial results. * Invesco Mortgage Capital Inc (IVR) qtrly basic earnings of $0.78 per common share. * Invesco Mortgage Capital Inc (IVR) qtrly core earnings of $0.40 per common share. * Q1 earnings per share view $0.39 -- Thomson Reuters I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:

















                                                    Invesco Mortgage Capital Inc. Reports First Quarter 2017 Financial Results
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    4:15 PM ET 05/04/2017
                                                


ATLANTA, May 4, 2017  Invesco Mortgage Capital Inc. (IVR) today announced financial results for the quarter ended March 31, 2017, reporting basic earnings of $0.78 per common share, core earnings* of $0.40 per common share and book value per diluted common share** of $17.95.












